<p>Guess what is just around the corner?? MONKEYS! Ehhh, I&nbsp; mean <a href="kidsfair.html">Kids-Fair
2000!</a>&nbsp; You've been hearing a lot about it, and now is the time
to get excited for old and young kids alike. Kids-Fair is a unique event
that brings together all our schools, kids, many student groups, and the
community for a day of sharing and learning.&nbsp; Not to mention that
there will be a lot of fun, prizes, and guest appearances!&nbsp;
<center>
<p><a href="kidsfair/buddy.html"><img SRC="buddies.gif" BORDER=0 height=145 width=240></a></center>

<p>Right now we need you to sign-up as a <a href="kidsfair/buddy.html">Kids-Fair
Buddy</a>! ANYONE CAN BE A BUDDY!&nbsp; PLEASE sign-up yourself and any
friends for any amount of time.&nbsp; It's worth it!
<p>After touring through our site, please sign our <a href="cgi-data/guestbook.html">Guestbook</a>
to tell us what you think about our program.&nbsp; We look forward to seeing
you soon at the Kids-Fair 2000!
<p>-Rishi, Lee, Sara, and E
